  "title": "Locum Staff Nurse",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>General nursing duties in clinic which include preparing patients for their health screening.</li><li>Handle any registration, appointment bookings and answer any phone call enquiries</li><li>Follow up with patients on any feedback / concerns that they may have</li><li>Interact and coordinate with different teams to ensure that the centre's operations is running smoothly and\nefficiently</li><li>Provide administrative support to the department when required.</li><li>Any other adhoc duties as assigned by the Clinic Manager</li><li>Recognized qualification in nursing field</li><li>Candidates with blood taking or iv cannulation experience will have added advantage</li><li>At least 2 year(s) of working experience in related field is required for this position with</li><li>Willing to do onsite event.</li><li>Part time</li><li>Must be Registered with valid SNB</li><li>Must be able to perform cannulation</li></ul><p>Applicants who are interested in this role are invited to apply with their comprehensive resume with full details via <strong>\"Apply Now\" </strong>button. Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
